abstract: Google says it will soon begin testing a long-awaited system that can block unauthorized copyrighted clips from being uploaded to YouTube.
snippet: Google says it will soon begin testing a long-awaited system that can block unauthorized copyrighted clips from being uploaded to YouTube.
lead_paragraph: Google says it will soon begin testing a long-awaited system that can block unauthorized copyrighted clips from being uploaded to YouTube, the popular video-sharing site it bought last year.

headline.main: YouTube Sets Tests of Video Blocking
headline.print_headline: YouTube Sets Tests of Video Blocking

abstract: Terry S. Semel, Yahoo’s chief executive, is facing mounting questions about internal morale problems.
snippet: Terry S. Semel, Yahoo’s chief executive, is facing mounting questions about internal morale problems.
lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO, June 11  When Terry S. Semel, Yahoo’s chief executive, faces shareholders at the company’s annual meeting on Tuesday, Eric Jackson will be there to pepper him with questions.

headline.main: For Yahoo, an Ordeal of Dissent
headline.print_headline: For Yahoo, An Ordeal Of Discord
